version_description: This is similar to other versions changing the C chord in others to Cadd9 which I think sounds better and adding the D Dsus4 Dsus2 D "flicker" to the verse.
a few chords missing in other versions
My version uses the Cadd9 chord used in the original song, which I haven't seen used in previously submitted versions.
This version has the guitar solo tabs and it has a Cadd9 instead of C, and D, Dsus4, D2 instead of D to be more accurate.
